ss\", \"score\": 0.9942031305340098, \"rank\": 0.005830669086188953, \"text\": \"Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now it's just really exciting to see it happen.\\\"\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith, who took gold in the 100 breaststroke, settled for a silver this time in 2:19.60.\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The bronze went to Tes Schouten (2:21.05) of the Netherlands.\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2357, \"end\": 2365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willem_Schouten\", \"score\": 0.9801430663935535, \"rank\": 0.01991844521922957, \"text\": \"Schouten\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willem_Schouten\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Willem_Schouten\"}, {\"begin\": 2383, \"end\": 2394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7813930272977445, \"rank\": 0.2795829903760127, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"King, the winner of five medals including two golds at the last two Olympics, failed to claim an individual prize in her Olympic farewell.\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She tied for fourth in the 100 breaststroke and finished more than 6 1/2 seconds behind Douglass in the 200.\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2624, \"end\": 2632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"score\": 0.9942031305340098, \"rank\": 0.005